description: Brain Scientific Inc., a medtech company, provides neurology-focused medical devices and electric motors in the United States. The company also develops motor platforms; an ultra-precise micro dosing pump; and motion products. The company offers NeuroCap, a disposable and soft layered cap with an integrated electrode circuit that is designed to address existing problems of conventional EEG systems; and NeuroEEG, a clinical-grade device for prescription use to acquire, record, transmit, and display electrical brain activity for patients of all ages, as well as NeuroNet Cloud, a database where brain data can be stored and analyzed. Brain Scientific Inc. was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Sarasota, Florida.
